    <item>
      <title>Specification</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/docs/specification/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/docs/specification/</guid>
      <description>
        
        
        &lt;h1&gt;Asset–Task Flow Specification&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Version:&lt;/strong&gt; 1.0.0
&lt;strong&gt;Status:&lt;/strong&gt; Draft&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The key words &amp;ldquo;MUST&amp;rdquo;, &amp;ldquo;MUST NOT&amp;rdquo;, &amp;ldquo;REQUIRED&amp;rdquo;, &amp;ldquo;SHALL&amp;rdquo;, &amp;ldquo;SHALL NOT&amp;rdquo;, &amp;ldquo;SHOULD&amp;rdquo;, &amp;ldquo;SHOULD NOT&amp;rdquo;, &amp;ldquo;RECOMMENDED&amp;rdquo;, &amp;ldquo;MAY&amp;rdquo;, and &amp;ldquo;OPTIONAL&amp;rdquo; in this document are to be interpreted as described in &lt;a href=&#34;https://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc2119&#34;target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;RFC 2119&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;1. Assets&lt;span class=&#34;hx:absolute hx:-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;1-assets&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#1-assets&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3&gt;1.1 Definition&lt;span class=&#34;hx:absolute hx:-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;11-definition&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#11-definition&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;An Asset MUST be a uniquely identifiable entity within the system.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;1.2 Identification&lt;span class=&#34;hx:absolute hx:-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;12-identification&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#12-identification&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;Each Asset MUST have a unique identifier (Asset ID).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;2. Tasks&lt;span class=&#34;hx:absolute hx:-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;2-tasks&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#2-tasks&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3&gt;2.1 Definition&lt;span class=&#34;hx:absolute hx:-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;21-definition&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#21-definition&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;A Task MUST represent a discrete unit of work.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;2.2 Linking&lt;span class=&#34;hx:absolute hx:-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;22-linking&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#22-linking&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;Every Task MUST be linked to at least one Asset. If a Task affects multiple Assets, it SHOULD be split into sub-tasks or linked to a parent Asset that encompasses the affected components.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;2.3 Typing&lt;span class=&#34;hx:absolute hx:-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;23-typing&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#23-typing&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;Every Task MUST be assigned exactly one of the following Task Types:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;Flow&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;Flowless&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;Ad Hoc&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;3. Flow&lt;span class=&#34;hx:absolute hx:-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;3-flow&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#3-flow&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3&gt;3.1 Measurement&lt;span class=&#34;hx:absolute hx:-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;31-measurement&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#31-measurement&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;Flow MUST be measured by the completion of Flow Tasks.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;3.2 Metrics&lt;span class=&#34;hx:absolute hx:-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;32-metrics&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#32-metrics&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;Implementers SHOULD track the ratio of Flow Tasks to Flowless Tasks to determine the &amp;ldquo;Operational Efficiency&amp;rdquo; of the system.&lt;/p&gt;

      </description>
    </item>
    
